data.description: Discover the epitome of luxurious living with this exquisite ground-floor, corner residence nestled within the prestigious coach home community of The Oaks at Whiskey Creek! This stunning home showcases 9ft ceilings and a generously proportioned gathering room, offering endless possibilities. Indulge in the comfort and convenience of a thoughtfully designed split floor plan that encompasses three inviting bedrooms and two full bathrooms. The master suite is a true sanctuary, featuring two walk-in closets and an ensuite bathroom with its double sinks and tastefully tiled shower. The open kitchen is well-appointed with stainless steel appliances and granite countertops. An attached, extended kitchen island provides extra seating and serving space, making it perfect for entertaining guests. Enjoy the shaded, private, screened-in lanai, perfect for outdoor relaxation. The attached 1-car garage, beautifully paved driveway and private owners entrance provide charming entry option. On those bright and sunny days, you can enjoy the outdoor space Whiskey Creek has to offer or cool off and relax at the community pool and spa. This pet-friendly, pool community features beautiful architectural details, including barrel tile roofs. In the heart of it all, offering quick access to restaurants, shopping, entertainment, and is just a short 10-mile drive to Fort Myers Beach.
